        <body>
            <div type="question">
                <p>What are your daily habits? What time do you get up, etc.?</p>
                <note type="word-limit">(at least 30 words)</note>
                <label type="level">
                    <span>A1</span>
                </label>
            </div>
            <div type="answer">
                <p>I get up at 7am and I take a shower! This very important if I want to feel me awake. Every morning I look at my Facebook and I wish &quot;happy birthday&quot; to my friends.</p>
                <p>Then I take a breakfast. Food it's my life!! I never forget to brush my teeths.</p>
                <p>I take the bus to University going.</p>
                <p>The evening I play sport.</p>
            </div>
